Run the inference proxy or provider server

Usage: soma inference <COMMAND>

Commands:
  serve  Run the provider-side server
  proxy  Run the local agent-facing proxy on `127.0.0.1:<port>`
  help   Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help

EXAMPLES:
    soma inference serve --config provider.toml
    soma inference proxy --config client.toml
